CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 8, 1947, pg. 3, reads: "Delta Soror Honored - Mrs. Daisy Lampkin, who was recently made an honorary member of Delta Sigma Theta Sorority received high tribute last week when David Filner of the Centre Avenue Bakery delivered a huge cake at The Courier in honor of the noted NAACP leader and Courier vice president... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Daisy Lampkin cutting and serving cake from Centre Avenue bakery, surrounded by other women, in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper office with maps on wall in background
